appeal_case
Disk World creator help
appeal_case

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
appeal_case -  This method sets the case as reopened for an appeal.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int appeal_case(string area,
int id,
string appealer,
string reason)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area the case is in
%^BOLD%^id%^RESET%^ - the of the case to appeal
%^BOLD%^appealer%^RESET%^ - the person who does the appeal
%^BOLD%^reason%^RESET%^ - the reason for the appeal
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/inherit/case_control.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the case as reopened for an appeal.  After an appeal
the case will be closed again.
.EP

